      • setSourceEndpoint

        public FileTypes.AddSpec.Builder setSourceEndpoint(TransferEndpoint sourceEndpoint)
        Location from which the Content Library Service will fetch the file, rather than requiring a client to upload the file. This property is optional and it is only relevant when the value of getSourceType() is FileTypes.SourceType.PULL.
        Parameters:
        sourceEndpoint - New value for the property.

      • setSize

        public FileTypes.AddSpec.Builder setSize(java.lang.Long size)
        The file size, in bytes. If null, the server will not verify it received the correct size.
        Parameters:
        size - New value for the property.

      • setChecksumInfo

        public FileTypes.AddSpec.Builder setChecksumInfo(FileTypes.ChecksumInfo checksumInfo)
        The checksum of the file. If specified, the server will verify the checksum once the file is received. If there is a mismatch, the upload will fail. For ova files, this value should not be set. If null, the server will not verify the checksum.
        Parameters:
        checksumInfo - New value for the property.
